@nickwallen 

Re: license. The GeoLite2 databases are fine license-wise (CC-BY) and have attribution.  If it were the commercial/enterprise DBs, we wouldn't be able to include them as they're under a separate license.

The review comments should be addressed, but obviously let me know if you want any adjustments or if I missed anything.  There was a lot of good stuff and I'm glad you went over things thoroughly.
